Privacy Policy

Last updated: July 11, 2026

Overview

Tic-Tac-Toe Two Player is a tic tac toe game for Apple Watch. This policy is short because the app does not collect any data.

Data Collection

Tic-Tac-Toe Two Player does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. Specifically:


No personal data is collected
No usage or analytics data is collected
No advertising identifiers are used
No third-party services, SDKs, or trackers are included
No account or sign-in is required


Data Stored on Your Device

Game preferences, such as your selected theme, are stored locally on your device only. This information never leaves your device and is deleted when you uninstall the app.

Children's Privacy

Because the app collects no data from anyone, it collects no data from children.

Changes to This Policy

If this policy ever changes (for example, if a future update adds new features), the updated policy will be posted at this page with a new date.

